info.name: Kaju Burfi
info.description: Kaju burfi has a rich, buttery, and mildly sweet flavor. The primary taste comes from the cashew nuts themselves, which have a naturally sweet and nutty profile. Some variations may include additional flavors such as saffron or cardamom for added depth.
